===Ground a part=== <!--T:47-->

<!--T:48-->
To keep the assembly at the desired position, the base part should be locked, or grounded as it is called here. Select the Base in the [[Tree_view|Tree view]] or in the [[3D_view|3D view]] and use the [[Image:Assembly_ToggleGrounded.svg|24px]] [[Assembly_ToggleGrounded|Toggle grounded]] command. This fixes the position of the Base in relation to the local coordinate system (LCS) of the Assembly container. A GroundedJoint object is added to the Joints container.

</translate>
